title: NHTSA, Toyota Corolla complaints: injury or death, 1991 to 2010, USA
name: NHTSA, Toyota Corolla complaints: injury or death, 1991 to 2010, USA
description: The point shapefile shows complaints about Corrolla's safety by location of the dealership's city. These complaints occurred between 1991 and Jan 2010. The NHTSA data is a comma delimited flat file of over 100Mb that includes complaints related to all car manufacturers between 1991-2010. Extracted data for Toyota and filtered out records for Corolla that has one or more injury or death.
